ZH: 无论你去哪里，我都会支持你。
EN: Wherever you go, I will always support you.

ZH: 无论是好是坏，我都会接受。
EN: Whether it's good or bad, I will accept it.

ZH: 无论多困难，我们都要坚持下去。
EN: No matter how difficult it is, we must persevere.

ZH: 无论多忙，我都会抽出时间来看望你。
EN: No matter how busy I am, I will make time to visit you.

ZH: 无论天气如何，我们都要出发。
EN: Regardless of the weather, we have to set off.

ZH: 无论他是否同意，我们都会继续下去。
EN: Whether he agrees or not, we will continue.

ZH: 无论结果如何，我们都要尽力而为。
EN: No matter what the outcome is, we must do our best.

ZH: 无论他说什么，我都不会改变主意。
EN: Whatever he says, I will not change my mind.

ZH: 无论你带什么，我都会高兴。
EN: Whatever you bring, I will be happy.

ZH: 无论多么困难，我们都要勇敢面对。
EN: No matter how difficult it is, we must face it bravely.

ZH: 无论他做错了什么，我们都必须原谅他。
EN: Whatever he did wrong, we must forgive him.

ZH: 无论我做什么，你都不会感到孤单。
EN: Whatever I do, you will never feel lonely.

ZH: 无论多么可能，我们都要抱有希望。
EN: No matter how unlikely it is, we must hold on to hope.

ZH: 无论你选择哪个，我都会支持你。
EN: Whichever one you choose, I will support you.

ZH: 无论你有多少困难，我们都会一起面对。
EN: No matter how many difficulties you have, we will face them together.

ZH: 无论是早是晚，我们都会准时出发。
EN: Whether it's early or late, we will depart on time.

ZH: 无论他有什么困难，我们都会提供帮助。
EN: Whatever difficulties he has, we will provide assistance.

ZH: 无论多糟糕的情况，我们都要挺过去。
EN: No matter how bad the situation is, we have to get through it.

ZH: 无论你需要什么，我都会尽力满足。
EN: Whatever you need, I will try my best to fulfill.

ZH: 无论我们走多远，我们都要一起走下去。
EN: No matter how far we go, we must walk together.
